## Python Backend and React Frontend Class

Separating the Backend and the Frontend is highly recommended in the industry. It is easy to maintain

### Build api in your python application that shares backend data as a json file or xml file

### Benefit of REST APIs
Provides developers with the ability to organize complicated applications into simple resources
It makes it easier for external clients to build on your REST API without any complications
It is very easy to scale;

### Build you React application to consume those data sent as json file from the backend



